</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Current Applications and Future Directions for the CDISC Operational Data Model Standard: A Methodological Review</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hume%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Sam Hume</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Sam Hume</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a</sup>Dakota State University, College of Business and Information Systems, 820 N Washington Ave, Madison, SD 57042</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hume%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Sam Hume</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>a,</sup><sup>*</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Aerts%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Jozef Aerts</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Jozef Aerts</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>b</sup>FH Joanneum University of Applied Sciences, Eggenberger Allee 11, 8020 Graz, Austria</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Aerts%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Jozef Aerts</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>b</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sarnikar%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Surendra Sarnikar</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Surendra Sarnikar</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a</sup>Dakota State University, College of Business and Information Systems, 820 N Washington Ave, Madison, SD 57042</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sarnikar%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Surendra Sarnikar</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>a</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Huser%20V"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Vojtech Huser</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">Vojtech Huser</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>c</sup>Lister Hill National Center for Biomedical Communications, National Library of Medicine, National Institutes of Health, Bethesda, Maryland, 8600 Rockville Pike, Bld 38a, Rm 9N919, Bethesda, MD 20894</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Huser%20V"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Vojtech Huser</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>c</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
