<li id="R4">
<span class="label">4.</span><cite>FDA; D.o.H.a.H. Services, editor. United States Government: Federal Register. 2013. Transport Format for the Submission of Regulatory Study Data; Notice of Pilot Project; pp. 70954–70955.</cite> [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=United%20States%20Government:%20Federal%20Register&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R5">
<span class="label">5.</span><cite>ONC. The Standards and Interoperability Framework. 2015 Jan 27;2015 Available from:  <a href="http://wiki.siframework.org/" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://wiki.siframework.org/</a></cite> [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=The%20Standards%20and%20Interoperability%20Framework&amp;volume=2015&amp;publication_year=2015&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R6">
